{
  "texts": [
    "Performance and security are significantly important in the storage and sharing of patient data.",
    "While storing data in a cloud-based environment is a disadvantage in terms of data security [8], storing it on the blockchain is disadvantageous in terms of performance [9,10].Encrypting data before storing it to prevent it from falling into the hands of malicious persons is also one of the issues that negatively affects performance.",
    "The presence of central entities for storing and distributing patient data weakens the system against attacks from the inside or the outside.",
    "These entities that cause security vulnerabilities are included in many studies in the literature.",
    "Moreover, the authority of patients over their data is unclear [11,12]."
  ]
}